{"tid":906008,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"公斤定義變　棄砝碼改用電磁力秤","createTime":"2018-11-17T15:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T13:12:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"66dee4a3bab7e91867570cc50d730db3771b7388","tid":906008,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181117/20548093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548093&d=Ao7t8yvT3hs8ulZu38hyovM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=289c54c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F20548093&h=a4c42b83\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181117/20548093</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月17日 <br />\n<br />\n公斤定義變　棄砝碼改用電磁力秤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181117/large/a1206a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181117%2Flarge%2Fa1206a.gif&h=cd5fe458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨天在法國凡爾賽舉行的國際度量衡大會，正式通過改變質量單位公斤的定義方法，由實體改為以物理學常數來定義甚麼是一公斤，是長度、時間、溫度等度量衡公制七大基本單位最後一個擺脫實體定義。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以物理學常數精確計算<br />\n<br />\n自1889年來，想準確量度一公斤，就要拿法國收藏的「國際公斤原器」出來度一度，可是這個被暱稱為「大K」的鉑銥合金標準砝碼，跟世界各地複製品的質量漸見出入，按計算流失了50微克的質量，雖只是一粒沙左右，但在製藥、納米技術和精準工程等追求高準確測量的世界，這樣的誤差已不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n為擺脫標準砝碼實際質量會出現不穩的問題，科學家推動改以物理學常數來定義公斤。透過基布爾秤（Kibble balance）以電流產生的電磁力秤重，由於電流可以準確測量，質量亦可準確計算出來，將是普朗克常數（Planck's constant）的某個倍數，任何有基布爾秤的地方，都可用這統一標準準確量度質量。大會昨天決定除了改變公斤的定義方式，亦一錘定音確認近年實驗測出的普朗克常數詳細數值，但一公斤具體是普朗克常數的多少倍，尚待明年測量後敲定。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n新技術測智障風險　可篩選試管嬰</blockquote>"},{"pid":"fbce67c62538ba1fade9ce7e14ab0c67d0a8039d","tid":906008,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"竟然有野會冇Uncertainty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7a4ddec5a25779d0178fa8fa7ba49a5b178d05","tid":906008,"uid":13856,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T01:54:17.000Z","msg":"完全睇唔明"},{"pid":"a405638b9009bebe8b0cf8dda0a4519df49d2999","tid":906008,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"Kilograms 由ampere 計？"},{"pid":"dfdbb267b4a950d4ecfde19a51620a5ef9406839","tid":906008,"uid":57410,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"a405638b9009bebe8b0cf8dda0a4519df49d2999","tid":906008,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"Kilograms 由ampere 計？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"首先你要知道 基布爾秤Kibble balance係咩<br />\n有人想知我再講"},{"pid":"ed65c02cab1daef6d2987c073fdd27cfa450171d","tid":906008,"uid":102179,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dfdbb267b4a950d4ecfde19a51620a5ef9406839","tid":906008,"uid":57410,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"a405638b9009bebe8b0cf8dda0a4519df49d2999","tid":906008,"uid":23087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:00:11.000Z","msg":"Kilograms 由ampere 計？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"首先你要知道 基布爾秤Kibble balance係咩<br />\n有人想知我再講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:25:56.000Z","msg":"好撚想知呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"4b18666ae61af9271cf2b06fd6f5c374ad9ac962","tid":906008,"uid":56497,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c_e1wITe_ig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc_e1wITe_ig&d=Ao7t8yvT3hs8ulZu38hyovM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=b4f3ff57\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c_e1wITe_ig</a><br />\n講解得好詳細"},{"pid":"dce94a3291e80388de8856d89e1c050347ff5eef","tid":906008,"uid":121130,"like":1,"dislike":8